{% comment %}
  Size Guide page section — EU/UK charts + how to measure
{% endcomment %}

<div class="info-page-header">
  <div class="page-container">
    <span class="section-label">Fit Guide</span>
    <h1>Size Guide</h1>
    <p class="info-page-header__lead">Find your perfect fit. Our pieces are designed in European sizing. Use the charts below to find your size.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="size-guide-page page-container">

  <div class="measure-section">
    <h2>How to Measure</h2>
    <div class="measure-grid">
      <div class="measure-item">
        <div class="measure-item__visual">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/><path d="M9 12h6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Bust / Chest</h3>
        <p>Measure around the fullest part of your chest, keeping the tape parallel to the floor. Keep it snug but not tight.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="measure-item">
        <div class="measure-item__visual">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Waist</h3>
        <p>Measure around your natural waistline — the narrowest part of your torso, usually about 1 inch above your belly button.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="measure-item">
        <div class="measure-item__visual">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8 6h8M8 12h8M8 18h8"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Hips</h3>
        <p>Measure around the fullest part of your hips and bottom, approximately 8 inches below your natural waist.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="measure-item">
        <div class="measure-item__visual">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 3v18M19 3v18M5 12h14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Height</h3>
        <p>Stand straight against a wall without shoes. Measure from the floor to the top of your head for the most accurate reading.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="size-table-section">
    <h2>Women's Clothing</h2>
    <p class="size-note">All measurements in centimetres.</p>
    <div class="size-table-wrapper">
