  <div class="size-fit-tips">
    <h2>Fit Notes by Category</h2>
    <div class="fit-tips-grid">
      <div class="fit-tip">
        <h3>Linen Collection</h3>
        <p>Designed for a relaxed, airy fit. Our linen pieces are cut slightly generous — if between sizes, you can go true to size or size down if you prefer a cleaner silhouette. Linen softens and breathes more with each wash.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fit-tip">
        <h3>Swimwear</h3>
        <p>Swimwear is fitted and designed to stay in place in and out of water. If you prefer more coverage or a looser feel, size up. The fabric has stretch for comfort but holds its shape well.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fit-tip">
        <h3>Festival Wear</h3>
        <p>Our festival pieces are cut for movement — loose, comfortable, and expressive. Sizing is relaxed across the range. If you want a more fitted look, size down by one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fit-tip">
        <h3>Accessories</h3>
        <p>Hats are one-size-fits-most with adjustable bands. Bags come in one size only — dimensions are listed on each product page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
